S.FORM: == badukuk == 瓦氏鳳尾蕨 akenek kanen ku badukuk. mangazuway a badukuk palamelen tu titi misakabi. siwkay nu babaungen badukuk sa, u lemangawan kuyni, taneng mukan, akenek. u kapahay a lami'. sabelen ku mangazuay a kaway , asu'. manamuh mukan ku Sakizaya. mauzip ku badukuk i buyubuyuan.

== badokok == 瓦氏鳳尾蕨 akenek kanen ko badokok. mangazoway a badokok palamelen to titi misakabi. siwkay no babaongen badokok sa, o lemangawan koyni, taneng mokan, akenek. o kapahay a lami'. sabelen ko mangazoay a kaway , aso'. manamoh mokan ko Sakizaya. maozip ko badokok i boyoboyoan.
